REF: https://github.com/OPENNETWORKINGLAB/flowvisor/wiki/Installation-from-Source


sudo apt-get install build-essential ant
sudo aptitude install openjdk-6-jdk

git clone git://github.com/OPENNETWORKINGLAB/flowvisor.git
(Please use branch 0.8-MAINT)

Create user 'flowvisor' and related group 'flowvisor' and then launch the
following command:
sudo make fvuser=flowvisor fvgroup=flowvisor install



